{
  "stem": "2713.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we see, maybe, it won't take too long, so we all go back together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But unfortunately, it didn't happen.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So the-- it wasn't for much-- yeah, but what-- what happened is the-- the worry my father had, because we couldn't receive any mail from them.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he started to worry terribly that what happened to them.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because there was no mail going there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And all we knew that they arrived all right home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But a week went by, two weeks, three weeks, and we didn't have any mail from them.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they were really-- he was really worrying.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- and I could see my father, what he was going through.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I suggest, once, to my father, that, if he would buy me a bicycle, I would go.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because I'm the youngest, and the Germans wouldn't do anything to a-- a young boy like this.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he didn't want to hear about it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my other brother, which was with us too, he-- he wouldn't go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was-- he was-- he was afraid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He realized, more than me, that it's not so easy.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But I loved bicycles.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I used to love-- I had a bicycle, always.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I loved the bicycle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my father wouldn't be interested in it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But then another couple weeks went by, and he didn't hear anything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I begged him, because I could see really what he was-- how he was suffering.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[CRYING]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So, [SOBBING] and he decided that he would buy me a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he bought me a bicycle.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I got up at 4:00 in the morning, because I told my father that I want to get up very early, because I was terribly scared at night.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was terribly scared at night.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
